  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/9a89d66cf44396d383aa8ba7f5efeaed.avif?t=1732532734\" width=616 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A unique art style inspired by estamps and feudal japan.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gardens to rake and to design wisely.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple solutions puzzles giving you freedom and creativity.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An adventure depicting the cruel and sometimes absurd world of work told through weird and funny characters.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design As You Please</h2>Each item bring a specific constraint. You will have to place them in the garden wisely.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/6660b35f4a33ecca0193868c26af8f4a.poster.avif?t=1732532734\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/6660b35f4a33ecca0193868c26af8f4a.webm?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/6660b35f4a33ecca0193868c26af8f4a.mp4?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Creative !</h2>As soon as you respect item rules, you can come up with your own solution<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/63f967569e6cd4829ecd7050d9e23a3a.poster.avif?t=1732532734\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/63f967569e6cd4829ecd7050d9e23a3a.webm?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/63f967569e6cd4829ecd7050d9e23a3a.mp4?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Begin Your Carriere</h2>Work For Various Clients. How Far Will You Go ?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/ca44ac78da13c3df7d4a1828c9057762.poster.avif?t=1732532734\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/ca44ac78da13c3df7d4a1828c9057762.webm?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354830/extras/ca44ac78da13c3df7d4a1828c9057762.mp4?t=1732532734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
